      "subheader": "Taming the Midgame",
      "audio":"84.mp3",
      "script":"What we have done here was no mean feat- we have effectively and absolutely solved the endgame. Now the task is to work backwards. Is there a way that we can comparably reduce the midgame? The answer is, in many cases, yes. Stay tuned, because we will start to get a feeling of the shape of certain weakly solved subtrees of Connect 4."
